name: Spruce imprint
description:
My very first handcrafted spruce imprint, that I made on January 19, 2020. After many attempts, I was still able to achieve the result I wanted. And with this work, I decided to start the "Tree Prints" series, which I will digitalize using high-quality scanning and then turn into NFT. And first of all, I want you to print out this work and decorate your house. Thus, we will continue the amazing path of this spruce, even after its end. 

This spruce was approximately 45-55 years old. The print was made on acid-free paper using linocut ink.

| 6664x9152 pixels, 400 DPI |
